snippet.title: Unknown 9: Awakening - Official Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Unknown 9: Awakening is an action-adventure game where you play as Haroona, a Quaestor born with the ability to venture into a mysterious dimension that overlaps our own, known only as the Fold.

Unknown 9: Awakening is coming to PlayStation, Xbox, and PC in Fall 2024.

#IGN #Gaming
